\id 1CO - Dawro 
\h 1 Qoronttoosa 
\toc3 1Qo 
\toc2 1 Qoronttoosa 
\toc1 1 Qoronttoosa 
\mt2 Phawuloosi 
\mt1 Qoronttoosa Asaw 
\mt2 Xaafeedda Koyro Kiitaa 
\imt1 Geluwaa 
\ip Phawuloosi Qoronttoosa asaw xaafeedda koyro kiitay, Phawuloosi Qoronttoosa katamaan de7iyaa ammaniyaawanttu giddon Kiristtinnaa de7uwaanne ammanuwaa xeelliyaabaan denddeedda metuwaa dhayissanaw qoppiide xaafeeddawaa. He wode Qoronttoosa katamay he gaden de7iyaa asay go77ettiyaa eretteedda Giriike katamaa. Hewaa bollaakka qassi Akaayiyaa geetettiyaa Roomaa kawutethaassi huuphe katamaa. Ha katamay wolqqaama zali77iyaan, gami77iide minneedda wogaan, loythi aakki aakki biyaa yeda de7uwan woy giigennabaa haniyaawaaninne haymaanotiyaa coratethaan eretteeddawaa. 
\ip Yesuusi kiitteeddawe minissiide odanaw koyyeeddawe, he ammaniyaawanttu giddon de7iyaa shaakotethaabaanne yeda de7uwaabaa, woshummaabaanne geluwaa akaabaa, woosa golle wogaabaa, Geeshsha Ayyaanaa imotatuwaabaanne hayquwaa dendduwaabaa. Yesuusi kiitteeddawe ha Mishiraachchuwaa Qaalaa ha ooshatuwaa bolla minnisiide odiyaawaa naagiide shiishshee. 
\ip Siiquu Xoossay bare asaassi immeedda imotaa ubbaappe aadhdhiyaawaa gidiyaawaa odiyaa shemppuwaa tammanne heezzuu, ha maxaafan daro eretteeddawaa geetettiide qofettee. 
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwaassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa 
\io1 Geluwaa (1:1-9) 
\io1 Ammaniyaawanttu Giddon denddeedda shaakotethaa (1:10-4:21) 
\io1 Yeda de7uwaabaanne soy asaa de7uwaabaa (5:1-7:40) 
\io1 Ammaniyaawanttanne kiristtinna ammanuwaa akkibeennawantta (8:1-11:1) 
\io1 Ammaniyaawanttu de7uwaanne goshetaa wogaa (11:2-14:40) 
\io1 Kiristtoosi hayquwaa xooni denddowaanne ammaniyaawanttu dendduwaabaa (15:1-58) 
\io1 Yihudaan de7iyaa meetootanchchatuwassi imetteedda maaduwaabaa (16:1-4) 
\io1 Wurssethaa qutiyaa (16:5-24) 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Taani, Xoossaa sheniyaan Yesuusi Kiristtoosi kiitteeddawaa gidanaw xeesetteedda Phawuloosinne, nu ishaa Sostteniisi,  
\v 2 Qoronttoosan de7iyaa Xoossaa ammaniyaa asatuwaassi, Yesuusi Kiristtoosan geeyyeeddawanttussinne, nuussi Godaa gidiyaa nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa sunthaa ubba sa7aan xeesiyaa ubbatuwaanna geeshsha gidanaw xeesetteeddawanttussi ha dabidaabbiyaa xaafeetto. 
\p  
\v 3 Xoossay, nu Aawuunne nu Goday Yesuusi Kiristtoosi hinttenttussi aadho keekatethaanne sarotethaa immo. 
\s1 Xoossaa Galatussaa 
\p  
\v 4 Xoossay Kiristtoosa Yesuusa bagganna hinttenttussi immeedda aadho keekatethaa diraw, taani ubba wode hinttenttussi Xoossaa galatay.  
\v 5-6 Taani Kiristtoosassi markkattiyaawe hinttenttun minneedda diraw, hintte ubbabaani, haasayaa ubbaan eratethaa ubbaan, aani duretteeddita.  
\v 7 Hawaadan hintte nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa yuussaa naagishshin, ayyaanaa imotaappe haray atto ittuunne hinttenttussi paccenna.  
\v 8 Qassi nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa gallassan hintte kadhee baynnawantta gidanaadan, wurssethay gakkanaw I hinttentta minissanawaa.  
\v 9 Bare Na7aa nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa ittippetethaw hinttentta xeeseedda Xoossay ammanetteeddawaa. 
\s1 Ammaniyaa Asaa Giddon Shaakotethay Medhettoppo 
\p  
\v 10 Shin taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, itti wozanaaninne itti qofaan ittippe gidanaappe attin, shaakotethay hintte giddon de7enna mala, hintte ubbay itti haasayaa haasayanaadan, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa sunthan taani hinttentta woossay.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, Qaloo7a soy asay hinttenttubaa, hintte giddon walassay de7iyaawaa, taw odeeddino.  
\v 12 Taani giyaawe hawaa; hinttenttu huuphiyan huuphiyan, “Taani Phawuloosawaa. Taani Aphiloosawaa. Taani Keefaawaa. \f + \fr 1:12 \fq Keefaa: \ft Hawe Griike sunthaa gidiide, bilethay zaallaa giyaawaa. Hara Geeshsha Maxaafatuwan Keefaa sunthay Phexiroosa.\f* Taani Kiristtoosawaa” yaagiita.  
\v 13 Kiristtoosi shaaketteeddee? Hinttenttu diraw, masqqaliyaa bolla misimaariyan dhishettiide kaqetteeddawe Phawuloose? Woy hintte Phawuloosassi gidanaw xammaqetteedditee? 
\p  
\v 14 Taani Qarisiphphoosappenne Gaayoosappe attin, hinttenttuppe oonanne xammaqabeenna diraw, Xoossaa galatay.  
\v 15 Hewaa diraw, ooninne hinttentta taw gidanaadan xammaqetteeddita gaanaw danddayenna.  
\v 16 Qassi, E, Isxxifaanoosa soy asaakka taani xammaqaaddi. Shin haraa gujjaade xammaqaadditanttonne wozanaa aathikke.  
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosi taana mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odana mala kiitteeddappe attin, xammaqana mala kiittibeenna; qassi Kiristtoosi masqqaliyaa bolla hayqqeeddawe mela gidenna mala, taani asaa aadhdheedda eratethaa qaalaan tamaarissikke. 
\s1 Kiristtoosi Xoossaa Aadhdheedda Eraanne Wolqqaa 
\p  
\v 18 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosi masqqaliyaa bolla hayqqeeddawaa odiyaa qaalay dhayiyaawanttussi eeyatethaa. Shin nuussi attiyaawanttussi Xoossaa wolqqaa.  
\v 19 Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Taani eranchchatuwaa aadhdheedda eratethaa 
\q2 bayizzana; 
\q1 qassi akeekanchchatuwaa akeekaakka dhayissana” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Isa 29:14\x* 
\v 20 Aadhdheedda eranchchay haqan de7ii? Higgiyaa tamaarissiyaawe haqan de7ii? Woy ha alamiyaa xoonanaw palumettiyaawanttu waananddinooshsha? Xoossay ha sa7aa aadho eratethay eeyatethaa gidiyaawaa besseedda! \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Yob 12:17; Isa 19:12; 33:18; 44:25\x* 
\p  
\v 21 Ayissi gooppe, asay bare huuphe aadho eratethaan barena Xoossaa erenna mala, Xoossay bare aadho eratethaan diggiide, nuuni odiyaa eeya qaalaan ammaniyaawantta ashshanaw qoppeedda.  
\v 22 Ayihudatuu malaataa oochchiino. Qassi Giriike asatuu aadho eratethaa wolqqaama koshshaa koyyiino.  
\v 23 Shin nuuni masqqaliyaa bolla misimaariyan dhishettiide kaqetteedda Kiristtoosabaa odeetto. Hewe Ayihudatuwaassi dhubo; qassi Ayihuda gidennawanttussi eeyatethaa.  
\v 24 Shin Xoossay xeeseeddawanttussi Ayihudatussikka Giriikatussikka nuuni odiyaa Xoossaa wolqqaynne A aadho eratethay Kiristtoosa.  
\v 25 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa eeyatethay asaa aadhdheedda eratethaappe aadhdhee; qassi A laafatethaa geetettiyaawekka asaa minotethaappe minnee. 
\p  
\v 26 Simmi taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, Xoossay hinttentta xeesiyaa wode hintte woysa mala asentto qoppite. Asaa qofaan hintte giddon aadho eranchchatuu, wolqqaamatuunne dhoqqa sheeshshatuu dara gidikkino.  
\v 27 Shin Xoossay aadhdheedda eranchchatuwaa yeellayanaw, alamiyaan de7iyaa eeyatuwaa dooreedda; qassi minatuwaa yeellayanaw, alamiyaan de7iyaa laafatuwaa dooreedda.  
\v 28 Xoossay ha alamiyaan wolqqaamabaa giide qoppiyaawaa dhayissanaw, ha alamiyaa maaddennabaa kadhettobaanne hanibeennabaa dooreedda.  
\v 29 Hewaa diraw, ooninne Xoossaa sinthan ceeqettanaw bessenna.  
\v 30 Shin Xoossay hinttenttussi Kiristtoosi Yesuusa de7uwaa udi immeedda. Kiristtoosi nuussi aadho eratethaa, xillotethaa, geeshshatethaanne atotethaa gideedda.  
\v 31 Hewaa diraw, Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Ceeqettiyaa uray 
\q2 ooninne Goday ootheeddawaan ceeqetto” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 1:31 \xt Erm 9:24\x* 
\c 2  
\s1 Nuuni Kiristtoosa Kaqaabaa Markkatteetto 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani Xoossaa tumatethaa xuuraa \f + \fr 2:1 \fq Xoossaa tumatethaa xuuraa: \ft Itti itti Geeshsha Maxaafaa bilethatuu, Xoossaabaa markkatethaa, yaagiino.\f* hinttenttussi odanaw hinttenttukko yeedda wode, dhoqqa qaalaaninne aadhdheedda eratethaan odanaw yabeykke.  
\v 2 Ayissi gooppe, taani hinttenttunna de7aadde, Yesuusi Kiristtoosappenne qassi masqqaliyaa bolla misimaariyan dhishettiide I kaqetteeddawaappe attin, harabaa erennaadan, ta qofaa qachchaaddi.  
\v 3 Taani daaburaaninne yashshaan daro kokkorssaan hinttenttunna de7aaddi.  
\v 4 Taani tamaarissiyaawaanne odiyaawaa Xoossaa Ayyaanaaninne wolqqaan qonccissayppe attin, ciimma gidiide aadhdheedda eratethaa qaalaana gidenna.  
\v 5 Hewaa diraw, hintte ammanuu Xoossaa wolqqaanappe attin, asaa aadho eratethaan zemppibeenna. 
\s1 Xoossaa Aadhdheedda Eraa 
\p  
\v 6 Nuuni ayyaanan wozanaamatuwaa giddon aadho eratethaa hasayeetto. Shin hewekka ha alamiyaa aadho eratethaa gidenna; woy ha alamiyaa mooddiyaa dhayiyaawanttu aadho eratethaa gidenna.  
\v 7 Shin nuuni odiyaa aadho eratethay, Xoossay kasetiide, cora wodiyaappe kase nu bonchchuwaassi dooreedda asaappe geemmeedda A xuuraa aadho eratethaa.  
\v 8 Ha alamiyaa mooddiyaawanttuppe ooninne ha aadho eratethaa eribeenna. Unttunttu ereeddawaa gidintto, bonchcho Godaa masqqaliyaa bolla misimaariyan dhishiide kaqqikkino.  
\v 9 Shin Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Ooninne ayfiyaan be7ibeennawe, 
\q1 haythankka sisibeennawe, 
\q1 qassi ooninne bare wozanaan qoppibeennawe 
\q2 Xoossay barena siiqiyaawanttussi giigisseeddawaa” 
\m giyaawaadan nuuni hasayeetto. \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Isa 64:4\x* 
\v 10 Xoossay bare xuura yewuwaa bare Ayyaanaan nuuna erisseedda; ayissi gooppe, Geeshsha Ayyaanay Xoossaabaa haray atto geemmeedda yewuwaa ubbaa biddee.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, asaan de7iyaa asaa ayyaanaappe attin, asaabaa eriyaawe oonee? Hawaadankka, qassi Xoossaabaa Xoossaa Ayyaanaappe attin, ooninne erenna.  
\v 12 Nuuni Xoossay nuussi immeeddabaa ubbaa eranaw I nuussi yeddeedda Ayyaanaa akkeeddoppe attin, alamiyaa ayyaanaa akkibeykko. 
\p  
\v 13 Nuuni ayyaanaa yewuwaa \f + \fr 2:13 \fq ayyaanaa yewuwaa: \ft Geeshsha Ayyanay immeedda qaalaa.\f* ayyaanaa yewuwaanna gathiide, Geeshsha Ayyaanay nuuna tamaarisseedda qaalaan hawaa haasayeettoppe attin, asaa aadho eratethay nuuna tamaarisseedda qaalaan haasayokko.  
\v 14 Shin Geeshsha Ayyaanay baynna asay Xoossaa Ayyaanaa yewuwaa akkenna; ayissi gooppe, hewe aw eeyatethaa. Yewuu Geeshsha Ayyaanan paacettiyaa diraw, I eranaw danddayenna.  
\v 15 Shin Geeshsha Ayyaanay de7iyaa asay ubbabaa shaakkee; shin I bare huuphew oonaninne shaakettenna.  
\v 16 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa maxaafay, 
\q1 “Godaa wozanaa eriyaawe oonee? 
\q2 A zoranaw danddayiyaawe oonee?” 
\m yaagee. Shin nuussi Kiristtoosa wozanay de7ee. \f + \fr 2:16 \fq nuussi Kiristtoosa wozanay de7ee: \ft Hawaa guussay, nuuni Kiristtoosi qoppiyaawaadan qoppeetto guussaa.\f*\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Isa 40:13\x* 
\c 3  
\s1 Xoossaa Kaalliyaawanttu Oosuwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani Geeshsha Ayyaanay de7iyaa asaassi haasayiyaawaadan, hinttenttussi haasayanaw danddayabeykke. Shin ha alamiyaa asaassi haasayiyaawaadaaninne ammanuwan minnibeenna Kiristtoosan de7iyaa guutha naanaa mala asaassi haasayiyaawaadan haasayaaddi.  
\v 2 Hinttenttu biro mino qumaa maanaw danddaybeenna diraw, taani hinttentta maathaa pakaaddi; haray atto, ha77ikka danddaybeykkita.  
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, hintte ha77ikka ha alamiyaa asaadan de7iita. Hinttenttu ha alamiyaa asaa gidiyaawaa hintte giddon de7iyaa qanaatiinne palumay erissennee? Qassi ha alamiyaa asaadan simerettiita.  
\v 4 Ayissi gooppe, hinttenttuppe ittuu, “Taani Phawuloosawaa” gooppe, haray qassi, “Taani Aphiloosawaa” gooppe, ha alamiyaa asaa mala gidikkitee? 
\p  
\v 5 Yaatina, Aphiloosi oonee? Phawuloosi oonee? Nuuni hinttentta ammantheedda Xoossaa kaalliyaawantta. Xoossay nuussi huuphiyan huuphiyan immeedda oosuwaa ootheetto.  
\v 6 Taani puutiyaa tokkaaddi; Aphiloosi haathaa ushsheedda; shin Xoossay puutiyaa dichcheedda.  
\v 7 Hewaa diraw, dichchiyaa Xoossaappe attin, tokkiyaawekka haathaa ushshiyaawekka ayaanne gidenna.  
\v 8 Tokkiyaawenne haathaa ushshiyaawe itti mala; shin Xoossay huuphiyan huuphiyan A daaburaa keenaa aw woytana.  
\v 9 Nuuni Xoossaassi ittippe oothiyaa A oosanchchatuwaa gidiyaa diraw, hintte A oosuwaa sa7aa. 
\p Qassikka hintte Xoossaa golliyaa.  
\v 10 Xoossay taw immeedda aadho keekatethaan eranchcha anaaxiyadan, golliyaa baasuwaa baasaaddi. Hara uray A bolla keexxee. Shin A bolla keexxiyaa ooninne wooti keexxintto, bare huuphew naagetto.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay Yesuusi Kiristtoosa xalalaa baaso oothiide wotheedda. Aappe hara baasuwaa baasanaw ooninne danddayenna.  
\v 12 Shin ha baasuwaa bolla ooninne worqqaan gidina, biraan gidina, al77o shuchchan gidina, mithaan gidina, gattan woy maqaan keexxooppe,  
\v 13 asaa ubbaa oosuu qoncciyaa kesanawaa. Ayissi gooppe, tamaan qonccana diraw, he gallassay asaa ubbaa oosuwaa bessana. Asay ubbay bare oosuwaa wooti ootheeddenttonne tamay paaccana.  
\v 14 Ooninne baasuwaa bolla keexxeedda oosuu minniide attooppe, I woytaa akkanawaa.  
\v 15 O oosuunne guudettooppe, he uray qohettana. I bare huuphew attana; shin tamaa giddoppe kessi akkowaadan attana. 
\p  
\v 16 Hinttenttu Xoossay aqiyaa geeshsha golliyaa gidiyaawaanne Xoossaa Ayyaanay hinttenttun de7iyaawaa erikkitee?  
\v 17 Ooninne Xoossaa geeshsha golliyaa kolooppe, Xoossay A kolana. Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay aqiyaa geeshsha golli geeshsha; he geeshsha golliikka hinttentta. 
\p  
\v 18 Ooninne bare huuphiyaa cimmoppo. Hinttenttuppe ooninne barena ha alamiyaan aadho eranchcha yaagiide qoppooppe, aadho eranchcha gidanaw, eeya gido.  
\v 19 Ayissi gooppe, ha alamiyaa aadho eratethay Xoossaa sinthan eeyatethaa. Xoossaa maxaafay, 
\q1 “Xoossay aadho eranchchatuwaa 
\q2 unttuntta unttunttu geniyan oyqqee” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Yob 5:13\x* 
\v 20 Qassi, 
\q1 “Aadhdheedda eranchchatuwaa qofaykka 
\q2 maaduu baynnawaa gidiyaawaa Goday eree” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Maz 94:11\x* 
\v 21 Hewaa diraw, ooninne asaan ceeqettoppo. Ayissi gooppe, ubbabaykka hinttewaa.  
\v 22 Phawuloosikka, Aphiloosikka, Keefaykka, \f + \fr 3:22 \fq Keefaa: \ft 1:12 ha sunthaw xaafetteedda bilethaanna ittuwaa.\f* ha alamiikka, de7uukka, hayquukka, ha77i de7iyaawekka, sinthappe yaanawekk, ubbaykka hinttewaa.  
\v 23 Hinttenttu Kiristtoosawantta; Kiristtoosikka Xoossawaa. 
\c 4  
\s1 Kiristtoosa Kaalliyaawantta 
\p  
\v 1 Asay nuuna Kiristtoosaw oothiyaawanttudaninne Xoossaa gollen de7iyaa Xuuraa naagiyaa asaadan qoppo.  
\v 2 Yaatiide he asatuu barenttu Godaassi ammanetteeddawantta gidiide, beettanaw koshshee.  
\v 3 Shin hintte woy haray ta bolla pirddooppe, aynne gidenna. Haray atto, taanikka ta huuphiyan pirddikke.  
\v 4 Ayissi gooppe, taani ta huuphiyan ayaanneekka eriyaabay baawa; shin taana hewe xillissenna. Taana pirddiyaawe Godaa.  
\v 5 Hewaa diraw, Goday dhumaani geemmeeddabaa poo7uwaa kessiyaawe, wozanaa qofaa qonccissiyaawe yaana wodii gakkanaassi O bollaninne oonanne pirddoppite. He wode, asay ubbay huuphiyan huuphiyan Xoossaappe sabaa demmanawaa. 
\p  
\v 6 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hinttenttuppe ooninne ittuu tamaarissiyaawaa sabbiide, haray tamaarissiyaawaa borenna mala, “Xoossaa maxaafan xaafetteeddawaa bonchcha” yaagiyaawaa hintte nuunanna tamaarana mala, hintte diraw, tabaanne Aphiloosabaa leemisuwadan odaaddi.  
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, haratuwappe neena oonee dhoqqisseeddawe? Neeni Xoossaappe akkabeennabay new ayee de7iyaawe? Yaatina, neeni akkeeddawaa gidooppe, ayissi akkabeennawaadan ceeqettay? 
\p  
\v 8 Ha77i hintte kalleeddita. Ha77i duretteeddita. Nuuni baynnaan hinterekka kawuteeddita. Nuunikka hinttenttunna kawutanaadan, hintte kawuteedditentto lo77a shin.  
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, taw malatiyaawaadan, nuuni ha sa7aassi, kiitanchchatuwassinne asaassi kaassaa gideedda diraw, Xoossay nuuna Yesuusi kiitteeddawantta hayquwassi pirddetteedda asaadan, ubbaappe wurssethaa ootheedda. 
\p  
\v 10 Nuuni Kiristtoosa diraw eeya, shin hintte Kiristtoosan aadhdheedda eranchcha. Nuuni daaburanchcha, shin hintte mina. Hinttenttu bonchchetteeddawantta, shin nuuni tooshetteeddawantta.  
\v 11 Ha wodii gakkanaassi, nuuni koshatteetto; saametteetto; kallotteetto; deshetteetto. Qassi de7iyaa sa7aa dhayiide yuuyyeetto.  
\v 12 Nuuni nu kushiyan oothiide daabureetto. Nuuna asay sheqqiyaa wode, anjjeetto. Nuuna yederssi yuuyyiyaa wodekka danddayeetto.  
\v 13 Nu bolla iitabaa haasayiyaa wode, nuuni lo77o qaalaa zaaretto. Nuuni hawaa gakkanaassikka, ha sa7aa pituwanne ubbabaa buuraa gideeddo. 
\p  
\v 14 Taani ta siiqiyaa naanaadan, hinttentta seeranaw hawaa xaafaaddippe attin, yeellayanaw xaafabeykke.  
\v 15 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosan hinttentta dichchiyaa tammu sha77a asay hinttenttussi de7ooppekka, hinttenttussi itti aawuwaappe haray baawa. Ayissi gooppe, taani mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa hinttenttussi aheeddawaadan, Kiristtoosa Yesuusan hinttenttussi aawuwaa gidaaddi.  
\v 16 Simmi taanaadan hanite yaagaade hinttentta woossay.  
\v 17 Hewaa diraw, Godan ammanetteedda ta siiqiyaa ta na7aa Ximootoosa hinttenttukko kiittaaddi. I ubba sa7aan de7iyaa ammaniyaa asaa ubbaw taani tamaarissiyaa Kiristtoosa Yesuusan de7iyaa ta ogiyaa hinttentta hassayissanawaa. 
\p  
\v 18 Taani hinttentta be7anaw hinttenttukko yeennabaa malatina, otorettiyaa itti itti asatuu de7iino.  
\v 19 Shin Goday gooppe, taani hinttenttukko ellekka baade he otorettiyaa asatuwaassi haasayaa gidennaan, unttunttu wolqqaa erana.  
\v 20 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa kawutethay Xoossaa wolqqaanappe attin, haasayaana gidenna.  
\v 21 Taani hinttenttukko muriyaa xam77aanna yooyee woy siiquwaannanne ashikke ayyaanaanna yoo? Haqawaa dooriitee? 
\c 5  
\s1 Ammaniyaa Asaa Giddon Oosetteedda Pokkobaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hinttenttu giddon pokko woshummaa oosuu de7iyaawe zigirettee; hewaa mala pokko woshummaa oosuu haray atto, Xoossaa ammanenna asaa giddoninne baawa. Ayissi gooppe, bare aawuwaa machchatto akkeedda asay de7ee. \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Zar 22:30\x* 
\v 2 Hinttenttukka otoretteeddita. Hewaappe hintte kayyottanaw bessennee? Hewaa mala pokko oosuwaa ootheedda bitani hintte giddoppe kichchanaw bessee. 
\p  
\v 3-4 Ayaa gidinakka taani ta asatethaan hinttenttunna de7ennaani dhayooppekka, ayyaanan hinttenttunna de7ay. Ha77i hinttenttunna de7iyaawaadan hanaade, hewaa mala oosuwaa ootheedda bitaniyaa bolla nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa sunthan pirddadiggaaddi. Hinttenttunne ta ayyaanay nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa wolqqaanna ittippe shiiqiide,  
\v 5 he bitaniyaa ayyaanay Godaa Yesuusi pirddaw yiyaa gallassan attana mala, nagaraan kumeedda A bollaa kolanaadan Seexaanaassi hintte immanaadan, taani pirddaaddi. 
\p  
\v 6 Hinttenttu ceequu lo77a gidenna. Guutha irshshuu munaqaa ubbaa denthiyaawaa erikkitee?  
\v 7 Hinttenttu ooratha gidana mala, nagaraa irshshuu caaleeddawaa kessite. Hinttenttu irshshuu baynna munaqaa mala. Ayissi gooppe, nu Paasigaa dorssay, Kiristtoosi yarshshetteedda. \x - \xo 5:7 \xt Kes 12:5\x* 
\v 8 Hewaa diraw, nuuni Ukithaa Baalaa suuretethaaninne tumatethaan bonchchanaappe attin, caala irshshuwan, iitatethaa irshshuwaaninne geellatethaa irshshuwan bonchchokko. \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Kes 13:7; Zar 16:3\x* 
\p  
\v 9 Woshummanaw qoppiyaawanttunna hintte ittippe gaytenna mala, hinttenttussi dabidaabbiyaa xaafaaddi. \f + \fr 5:9 \fq dabidaabbiyaa xaafaaddi: \ft Hawaa xaafanaappe kassenna Phawuloosi Qoronttoosa asaassi xaafeedda hara qoncciyaan erettibeenna dabidaabbii de7ee guussaa.\f* 
\v 10 Taani giyaawe ha alamiyaan de7iyaa woshummanaw qoppiyaawanttuppe woy yorattiyaawanttuppe, kayisotiyaawanttupenne woy eeqaw goyinniyaawanttuppe ubbakka shaakettana mala gidenna. Hewaa gidooppe, ha alamiyaappe hintte shaaketti baanaw bessee guussaa.  
\v 11 Shin ishatuwaa ha77i geetettiyaawanttuppe ittuunne woshummanaw qoppiyaawanttu woy miishshaw yorattiyaawanttu woy eeqaw goyinniyaawanttu woy asaa sunthaa bayzziyaawanttu woy mathottiyaawanttu woy wuu77iyaawanttunna hinttenttu ittippetethaa oothenna mala, taani hinttenttussi xaafaaddi. Hewanttu malaanna haray atto, qumaakka ittippe mooppite. 
\p  
\v 12 Ayissi gooppe, woosa golleppe karenna de7iyaawanttu bolla pirddanaw taana ayee gathii? Hinttenttu giddon woosa gollen de7iyaawanttu bollan hintte pirddikkiteeyee?  
\v 13 Shin karenna de7iyaawanttu bollan Xoossay pirddana. He iitabaa oothiyaa uraa hintte giddoppe kessidiggite. \x - \xo 5:13 \xt Zar 13:5; 17:7\x* 
\c 6  
\s1 Ammaniyaa Asaa Giddon De7iyaa Walassaa Wootiide Dhayissanaw Bessii? 
\p  
\v 1 Hinttenttuppe itti uraassi bare ishaanna mootuu de7iyaabaa gidooppe, ammaniyaawanttu bolla pirddettanawaa bashiide, ammanennawanttu bolla pirddettanaw waani xaliide bii?  
\v 2 Ammaniyaawanttu alamiyaa bolla pirddanawaa erikkitee? Yaatina, alamiyaa bolla hintte pirddanawantta gidooppe, ubbabaappe guuxxiyaawaa pirddanaw danddaykkitee?  
\v 3 Ha de7uwaabay atto shin, ammaniyaawanttu kiitanchchatuwaa bolla pirddanawaa erikkitee?  
\v 4 Yaatina, hinttentta ha alamiyaa de7uwaabaw pirdda golle buussay koshshooppe, ammaniyaa asay kadheedda asaan pirddissanaw afiitee?  
\v 5 Taani hinttentta yeellayanaw hawaa gay; hawaa gidanaw bessii? Hinttenttu giddon ishatuwaa sigethanaw danddayiyaa lo77o eranchcha asay ittuunne baawee?  
\v 6 Shin itti ishay yokko ishaa pirdda gollen mootiidde, he yewuwaa ammanenna asaan pirddissii? 
\p  
\v 7 Simmi ittu ittuwaa mootiyaawe hintte giddon de7ooppe, hewe hintte kunddeeddawaa bessee. Hewaappe hintte naaqettiyaawenne cimettiyaawe lo77ennee?  
\v 8 Shin hintte hintte huuphew ittu ittuwaa haray atto, hintte ishatuwaakka naaqqiitanne cimmiita. 
\p  
\v 9 Woy makkalanchchatuu Xoossaa kawutethaa laattennawaa erikkitee? Baloppite. Woshummanaw qoppiyaawanttu woy eeqaw goyinniyaawanttu woy woshummiyaawanttu woy attumawaa gidiide, attumawaanna gisiyaawanttu,  
\v 10 woy kayisatuu woy miishshaw yorattiyaawanttu woy mathottiyaawanttu woy asaa sunthaa bayzziyaawanttu woy bonqqiyaawanttu Xoossaa kawutethaa laattikkino.  
\v 11 Hinttenttuppekka itti itti asay hewanttu mala. Shin Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa sunthaaninne nu Xoossaa Ayyaanaan hintte meecettiide geeyyeeddita; qassi xilleeddita. 
\s1 Hinttenttu Asatethaa Xoossaa Bonchchuwaassi Peeshshite 
\p  
\v 12 Itti uray, “Taani koyyeeddabaa ubbaa oothanaw danddayay” gaana danddayee. Shin ubbaykka taana maaddenna. Taani koyyeeddabaa ubbaa oothanaw danddayay. Shin ayeenneekka taana mooddenna.  
\v 13 Qay haraykka, “Qumay uluwassa; uluukka qumaassa” gee. Shin Xoossay uluwaakka qumaakka dhayissana. Asaa asatethay Godaa Yesuusassappe attin, woshummaassa gidenna. Godaa Yesuusikka asaa asatethaassa.  
\v 14 Xoossay Godaa Yesuusa hayquwaappe dentheedda; qassi nuunakka hayquwaappe bare wolqqaan denthana. 
\p  
\v 15 Hinttenttu asatethay Kiristtoosa asatethaanna ittuwaa gidiyaawaa hintte erikkitee? Yaatina, taani Kiristtoosa asatethaanna ittuwaa gideeddawaa afaade, caaratti asatethaanna ittuwaa oothanaw bessii? Bessenna!  
\v 16 Woy caarattinna ittipetethaa medhdhiyaa uray izinna itti asatetha gidiyaawaa erikkitee? Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa maxaafay, “Unttunttu laa77atuu itti asho gidana” yaagee. \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Dom 2:24\x* 
\v 17 Shin Godaanna ittipetethaa medhdhiyaa uray ayyaanan aananna ittuwaa gidee. 
\p  
\v 18 Woshummaappe haakkite. Itti uray oothiyaa hara nagaraa ubbay A asatethaappe karenna de7ee; shin woshummiyaawe bare bollan nagaraa oothee.  
\v 19 Woy hintte bollay Xoossay hinttenttussi immeedda hinttenttun de7iyaa Geeshsha Ayyaanay aqiyaa geeshsha golliyaa gidiyaawaa erikkitee? Qassi hintte hintte huuphiyaassa gidikkita.  
\v 20 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay hinttentta gatiyaan shammeedda. Hewaa diraw, hintte asatethaan A bonchchite. 
\c 7  
\s1 Geluwaa Akaabaassi Ooshetteedda Ooshaanne Imetteedda Zaaruwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hinttenttu taw xaafeedda yewuwaassi attuma asay maccawunno bochchennentto lo77a.  
\v 2 Shin woshummaa gaasuwaa diraw, attuma asaassi huuphiyan huuphiyan machchatta de7uu. Qassi macca asaassikka huuphiyan huuphiyan asinay de7o. 
\p  
\v 3 Asinay bare machchattiw asinatethaan bessiyaabaa udo; qassi hewaadan, machchattakka bare asinaassi machchetethaan bessiyaabaa oothu.  
\v 4 Machchatta bare asatethaassi goda gidukku; shin izi asinay goda. Hawaadankka, qassi asinay bare asatethaassi godaa gidenna; shin A machchatta goda.  
\v 5 Hinttenttu hintte giddon Xoossaa woosaan genccanaw he wodiyaassi zoretan digettanaappe attin, ittu ittuwaa diggoppite. Hinttenttu hinttentta naagenna diraw, Seexaanay hinttentta paaccennaadan, ittippe de7ite.  
\v 6 Shin taani hinttentta hewaa hintte dosowaadan hanite gayippe attin, azazikke.  
\v 7 Taani asay ubbay taanaadan hanintto dosay. Shin Xoossay asaw huuphiyan huuphiyan dumma dumma imotaa immi wotheedda; ittuwaassi hawaadan, qassi yokkowassi hewaadan immi wotheedda. 
\p  
\v 8 Hewaa diraw, taani machchatto akkibeennawanttunne asinay hayqqo maccawanttu taanaadan coo de7iinontto, unttunttoo lo77a gay.  
\v 9 Shin amuwan guudettiyaawaappe akkiyawenne geliyaawe lo77a gidiyaa diraw, unttunttu barentta naaganaw danddayana dhayooppe, akkinonne gelino. 
\p  
\v 10-11 Machchatta bare asinaappe shaakettuppu. Shin shaakettooppenne gelennaan de7uu; woy bare asinaanna sigettu. Asinaykka bare machchatto yeddoppo yaagaade, akkeeddawanttanne geleeddawantta azazay. Shin hawaa azaziyaawe Godaappe attin, taana gidikke. 
\p  
\v 12 Taani haratuwaa hawaadan gay; Godaa gidenna. Ammanenna machchatta de7iyaa ammaniyaa asay ooninne de7ooppe, A machchatta aananna ittippe de7iyaawaa I dosooppe, izo yeddoppo.  
\v 13 Qassi ammanenna asinay de7iyaa ammaniyaa machchatta de7ooppe, izi asinay izinna ittippe de7iyaawaa iza dosooppe, aappe shaakettuppu.  
\v 14 Ayissi gooppe, ammanenna asinay bare ammaniyaa machchattinna de7iide geeyyeedda. Qassi ammanenna machchatta bare ammaniyaa asinaanna de7aade geeyyaaddu. Hewe baawentto, hinttenttu naanay tunaa; shin ha77i unttunttu geeshsha.  
\v 15 Shin ammanennawe shaakettana koyyooppe shaaketto. Ammaniyaa machchatto gidina, woy asinaa gidina, hawaa mala yewuwaan qashettikkino. Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay nuuna sarotethaan de7anaw xeeseedda.  
\v 16 Ammaniyaa machchattee, neeni ne asinaa ashshaninttonne O eri? Woy ammaniyaa asinaw neeni ne machchatto ashshaninttonne O eri? 
\s1 Xoossay Hinttentta Koyro Xeesiyaa Wode Hinttenttu De7iyaa Hanotaan De7ite 
\p  
\v 17 Gidooppenne, asay huuphiyan huuphiyan Goday aw immeeddawaadaninne qassi Xoossay barena xeeseeddawaadan de7o. Hewe ammaniyaa asaa ubbaa taani tamaarisseedda higgiyaa.  
\v 18 Ooninne qaxxaretti uttiide, Xoossaa ammaneeddawaa gidooppe, bare qaxxaraa mallaa diggoppo. Qassi ooninne qaxxarettennan de7iidde, Xoossaa ammaneeddawaa gidooppe qaxxarettoppo.  
\v 19 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa azazuwaa naaganaappe attin, qaxxarettina qaxxarettana dhayina allaallii baawa. 
\p  
\v 20 Asay huuphiyan huuphiyan Xoossay barena xeesiyaa wode de7iyaawaadan de7o.  
\v 21 Xoossay neena xeesiyaa wode neeni ayllee? Aynne baawa; shin neeni aylletethaappe kesanaw danddayooppe kesa.  
\v 22 Ayissi gooppe, aylle gidi utteedda asaa Goday xeesooppe, I Goday aylletethaappe kesseedda asa. Hawaadankka, aylle gidenna asaa Kiristtoosi xeesooppe, I Kiristtoosa aylle.  
\v 23 Xoossay hinttentta gatiyaan shammeedda. Asaa aylle gidoppite.  
\v 24 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, asay huuphiyan huuphiyan Xoossay A xeesiyaa wode de7iyaa de7uwaadan, Xoossaanna de7o. 
\s1 Geletti Akettibeennawanttubaanne Am77etuwaabaassi Ooshetteedda Ooshaa 
\p  
\v 25 Wodoratuwassi Goday taana azazeeddabay baawa. Shin taani Godaassi ammanetteeddawaa gideedda diraw, aappe maarotethaa akkeeddawaadan, hinttentta zoray.  
\v 26 Simmi ha77i metuwassi taw hawe lo77a malatee; asay hawaadan haniide de7ooppe lo77a.  
\v 27 Neeni machchatto akkadiggeeddawaa gidooppe, izo yeddanaw koyyoppa. Machchatto akkabeennawaa gidooppe, akkanaw koyyoppa.  
\v 28 Shin neeni machchatto akkooppe, nagaraa oothabeykka. Wodorattaakka asinaa gelooppe, nagaraa oothabeykku. Shin akettiyaawanttoonne gelettiyaawanttoo unttunttu de7uwan wolqqaama metuu de7ee. Taani hinttentta he metuwaappe ashshanaw koyyay. 
\p  
\v 29 Shin taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani giyaawe hawaa; wodii wureedda. Hawaappe sinthaw akkeedda asatuu, akkibeenna asaadan hanino.  
\v 30 Yeekkiyaawanttu yeekkennawaadan, nashettiyaawanttu nashettennawaadan, shammiyaawanttukka shammiide aynnee baynnawaadan,  
\v 31 ha alamiyaa de7uwan maadettiyaawanttu ubbakka maadettennawaadan hanino. Ayissi gooppe, ha alamiyaa de7uu attiyaawaa. 
\p  
\v 32 Hinttenttu hirggennan de7anawaa taani dosay. Akkibeennawe Godaa nashechchanaw koyyiyaa diraw, A oosuwaabaa qoppee.  
\v 33 Shin akkeeddawe bare machchatto nashechchanaw koyyiyaa diraw, sa7aabaa qoppee.  
\v 34 A qofay shaaketteedda. Asinaa gelabeenna wodoratta bare ashuwaaninne bare shemppuwaan geeyyanaw koyyiyaa diraw, Godaa oosuwaabaa qoppaw. Shin asinaa geleeddawunna bare asinaa nashechchanaw koyyiyaa diraw, sa7aabaa qoppaw. 
\p  
\v 35 Taani hawaa hinttentta maaddana mala gayippe attin, hinttentta dhubbanaw giikke. Shin hintte bessiyaawaadan de7iidde, Godaa oosuwaa hinttena immiide oothana mala koyyay. 
\p  
\v 36 Ooninne bare giigisseedda wodoratto akkiya wodii gakkina, barena naaganaw aw danddayettennaan ixxooppe, izo akko. I izo akkooppe, hewaan nagaray baawa.  
\v 37 Shin I bare wozanaan minnooppe, akkennaan gami77ana danddayee. Qassi barena naagiide, bare giigisseedda wodoratto akkennaan gami77ana gooppe, ooninne wolqqanthennaan bare wozanaan qofaa qachcheeddawaa gidooppe loytheedda.  
\v 38 Hewaa diraw, wodoratto akkiya uray loytheedda; qassi akkennawe ubba aathi loytheedda. 
\p  
\v 39 Asinaa geleedda mishiratta bare asinay de7eedda keenan aananna itteppe de7anaadan qashetta uttaaddu. Shin I hayqqooppe, Godaa ammaniyaa asaa oonanne gidooppe, bare doseedda asinaa gelanaw danddayaw.  
\v 40 Ta qofaa gidooppe, gelennaan de7antto, iza nashechchaan de7ana. Qassi taanan Xoossaa Ayyaanay de7iyaawaa taani eray. 
\c 8  
\s1 Eeqaassi Yarshshetteedda Qumaabaa 
\p  
\v 1 Eeqaassi yarshsheedda qumaabaa gidooppe, nuuni ubbaykka ereetto. Eray otorssee; shin siiquu ammanuwan dichchee.  
\v 2 Ooninne barew ittibaa eriyaawaa malatooppe, I biro eranaw bessiyaawaa eribeenna.  
\v 3 Shin ooninne Xoossaa siiqooppe, Xoossay A eree. 
\p  
\v 4 Hewaa diraw, eeqaw yarshsheedda qumaa muussaabaa gidooppe, eeqaa ubbay alamiyaan ayaanne gidennawaanne, itti Xoossaappe attin, haray baynnawaa nuuni ereetto.  
\v 5 Ayissi gooppe, cora xoossatuunne cora godatuu de7iino. Shin haray atto, saluwan gidina sa7aan gidina, xoossatuwaa geetettiyaawanttu de7ooppekka,  
\v 6 ubbabaa medhdheeddawe nuuni aw de7iyaawe, itti Xoossay, Aawuu, nuussi de7ee. Qassi ubbabay aani medhetteeddawenne nuuni aani de7iyaawe itti Goday, Yesuusi Kiristtoosikka nuussi de7ee. 
\p  
\v 7 Shin ha eray asaa ubbaw de7enna. Itti itti asatuu eeqaa doyyeedda diraw, ha77i gakkanawukka, “Eeqaw yarshsheedda qumaa” yaagiidde miino. Qassi unttunttu wozanay shuga gideeddawaan, unttunttoo ha qumaan tuneeddawaa malatee.  
\v 8 Shin qumay nuuna Xoossaakko shiiqanaadan maaddenna. Nuuni maana dhayinttokka nuussi aynnee paccenna; mooppennee nuussi aynnee gujettenna. 
\p  
\v 9 Shin hawe hintte hintte dosowaadan haniyaawe shugo ammanuwanna de7iyaawantta nagaraan yeggenna mala naagettite.  
\v 10 Ayissi gooppe, neeni eranchchay eeqaw yarshsheedda qumaa maanaw eeqaa golliyaan utteedda wode, shugo ammanuwanna de7iyaa itti asay neena be7ooppe, eeqaw yarshsheedda qumaa I maanaw A wozanay qoppenneeyee?  
\v 11 Hewaa gidooppe ha shugo ammanuwanna de7iyaa ne ishay, Kiristtoosi A diraw hayqqeeddawe, ne eraan bayee.  
\v 12 Hawaadankka, hintte hintte ishatuwaa naaqqiyaawaaninne unttunttu shugo wozanaa maythiyaawaan Kiristtoosa naaqqiita.  
\v 13 Hewaa diraw, qumay ammaniyaa ta ishaa dhubbiyaawaa gidooppe, A dhubbenna mala, ta de7iyaa laythaan mulekka ashuwaa miikke. 
\c 9  
\s1 Yesuusi Kiitteeddawanttussi De7iyaa Maataanne Unttunttu Oothanaw Bessiyaabaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taani aylletethay baynna asa gidikkitaa? Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa gidikkitaa? Nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa be7abeykkitaa? Hinttenttu taani Godaassi ootheedda ta oosuwaappe beetteeddawantta gidikkiteeyee?  
\v 2 Taani haranttussi Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa gidana dhayooppekka, hinttenttoo Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa gidiyaawe eretteeddawaa; ayissi gooppe, taani Godan Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa gidiyaawoo hintte markka. 
\p  
\v 3 Taana boriyaawanttussi taani immiyaa zaaruu hawaa.  
\v 4 Maanawunne ushanaw nuussi maati baawee?  
\v 5 Yesuusi kiitteedda haratuwaadaaninne Godaa ishatuwaadan, qassi Phexiroossawaadan, eeno giyaa machchatto ittippe akkiide baanaw nuussi maatay baawee?  
\v 6 Woy nu de7uwassi oothiidde baaxetanaw bessiyaawe taananne Barnaabaasa xalalee?  
\v 7 Ay wodenne bare miishshaa miidde, wottaaddaratethaa oothiyaawe oonee? Woy woyiniyaa turaa tokkiide, A ayfiyaa meennawe oonee? Woy miizza wudiyaa heemmiidde, he miizza wudiyaappe maathaa ushennawe oonee? 
\p  
\v 8 Taani hawaa asaa qofaa xalalaan gaytaa? Woy higgii qassi hawaa geennee?  
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, Muse Higgiyan, “Kathaa yedhdhiyaa mehiyaa doonaa qachchoppa” geetettiide xaafetteedda. Xoossay mehiyaabaa qoppiide hawaa gii? \x - \xo 9:9 \xt Zar 25:4; 1Xi 5:18\x* 
\v 10 Woy I hewaa giyaawe mulekka nu diraassa gidennee? Tumakka nu diraw xaafetteedda; goshiyaa bitaniikka kathaa bukkiyaa bitaniikka, “Taana gakkiyawaa akkana” yaagiidde oothanaw bessee.  
\v 11 Nuuni hintte giddon ayyaanaa yewuwaa zereeddawantta gidiide, nu ashuwaassi maado gidiyaawaa hinttenttuppe cakkooppe darobee?  
\v 12 Haratuu hewaa hinttenttuppe akkanaw unttunttoo maatay de7ooppe, nuussi unttunttuwaappe aadhdhiyaa maatay baawee? 
\p Shin nuuni Kiristtoosa mishiraachchuwaa qaalaassi dhubo gidennaadan, ubbabaa gencciyaawaappe attin, he maataan go77ettibeykko.  
\v 13 Geeshsha Golliyan oothiyaa asatuu barenttu qumaa Geeshsha Golliyaappe akkiyawaa erikkitee? Qassi yarshshiyaasaan oothiyaawanttu yarshshuwaappe akkiyawaa erikkitee? \x - \xo 9:13 \xt Zar 18:1\x* 
\v 14 Hawaadankka, qassi mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odiyaawanttu barenttu de7uwaassi koshshiyaabaa aappe demmanaadan, Goday azazeedda. 
\p  
\v 15 Shin taani ha maataa ubbaan aynne go77ettabeykke. Taani hawaa xaafeeddawe hewaa mala maatay taw de7anaw bessee yaagiyaawaana gidenna. Ayissi gooppe, ta ceequwaa ooninne mela kessiyaawaappe hayqqiyaawe taw lo77a.  
\v 16 Mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odanaw taani azazetta utteedda diraw, A odooppekka taw ceeqettiyaabay baawa. Mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odennaan aggooppe, taw aayyero.  
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, taani hawaa dosaade oothooppe, taw woytay de7ee. Shin taani dosennaan ixxooppekka, mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa diraw hadaraa Xoossay taw immeedda.  
\v 18 Yaatina, ta woytay ayee? Mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odaadde, taw wonggalaan de7iyaa kumentha maataan go77ettennan, mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa coo odiyaawaa. 
\p  
\v 19 Taani oossinne aylle gidikke shin, coratuwaa zaaranaw taana ubbaw aylle kessaaddi.  
\v 20 Taani Ayihudatuwaa zaaranaw unttunttunna unttuntta gidaade de7aaddi. Ta huuphew higgiyaappe garssanna de7ikke. Shin higgiyaappe garssanna de7iyaawantta zaaranaw higgiyaappe garssanna de7iyaa asaa mala gidaaddi.  
\v 21 Taani higgii baynna asatuwaanna de7aadde, higgii baynna asaadan hanaaddi. Xoossaa higgii dhayina gidenna. Shin higgii baynnawantta zaaranaw, Kiristtoosa higgiyaappe garssanna de7aaddi.  
\v 22 Taani ammanuwan daaburiyaawantta zaaranaw, unttunttu mala gidaaddi. Taani ay ogiyaaninne amareedda asatuwaa ashshanaw, ubba asatuwaanna ubbabaani unttunttu mala gidaaddi.  
\v 23 Taani mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa anjjuwaa shaakkanaw, mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa diraw, ubbabaa oothay. 
\p  
\v 24 Wothaan xoonana giide woxxiyaa ubbay ittippe woxxee. Shin ittuwaa xalalay woytaa akkiyawaa erikkitee? Hawaadan hinttenttukka woytaa akkanaw woxxite.  
\v 25 Kaassaw barena giigissiyaa ooninne ubbabaani barena naagee. Asay hewaa daaburiyaawe xooneeddawoo imettiyaa bayiyaa akliliyaa demmanaassa. Shin nuuni daaburiyaawe medhinaw de7iyaawaanne bayenna akliliyaa demmanaassa.  
\v 26 Hewaa diraw, taani qofi baynnaan woxxiyaawaadan woxxikke. Carkkuwaa yimppiyaa asaadankka coo olettikke.  
\v 27 Shin taani haranttoo odeeddawaappe guyyiyan, ta huuphew woytaappe attenna mala, ta asatethaa naagettanaadan oothay. 
\c 10  
\s1 Eeqaw Goyinnanaw Bessenna 
\p  
\v 1 Hewaa bollan taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani hintte hawaa erana mala koyyay. Nu aawotuu ubbay shaariyaappe garssanna de7eeddino; ubbaykka abbaa giddonna pinneeddino. \x - \xo 10:1 \xt Kes 13:21-22; 14:22-29\x* 
\v 2 Unttunttu ubbay Mussenna itteppe gidanaw, shaariyaaninne abbaan xammaqetteeddino.  
\v 3 Unttunttu ubbay he itti ayyaanaa qumaa meeddino. \x - \xo 10:3 \xt Kes 16:35\x* 
\v 4 Qassi ubbaykka he itti ayyaanaa ushshaa usheeddino. Ayissi gooppe, unttunttu barentta kaalethiyaa ayyaanaa zaallaappe pulttowaa usheeddino; he zaallaykka Kiristtoosa. \x - \xo 10:4 \xt Kes 17:6; Pay 20:11\x* 
\v 5 Shin Xoossay unttunttuppe dariya baggatuwan nashettibeenna diraw, unttunttu anhay asay baynna saan laaletteedda. \x - \xo 10:5 \xt Pay 14:29-30\x* 
\p  
\v 6 Unttunttu iitabaa amotteeddawaadan, nu wozanay qassi iitabaa amuwaappe naagettanaadan, hewe ubbay nuussi timirtte gideedda. \x - \xo 10:6 \xt Pay 11:4\x* 
\v 7 Xoossaa maxaafay, “Asay maanawunne ushanaw utteeddino; qassi duroo denddi eqqeeddino” yaagiyaawaadan, unttunttuppe ittu ittu eeqaw goyinneeddawaadan, hintte goyinnoppite. \x - \xo 10:7 \xt Kes 32:6\x* 
\v 8 Unttunttuppe ittu ittu woshummeeddawaadan, nuuni woshummanaw bessenna. Hewaa gaasuwan unttunttuppe itti gallassi laatamanne heezzu sha77ay hayqqeedda. \x - \xo 10:8 \xt Pay 25:1-18\x* 
\v 9 Unttunttuppe ittu ittu Godaa paacciide, shooshshaan duketti hayqqeeddawaadan, nuuni Godaa paaccanaw bessenna.  
\v 10 Unttunttuppe ittu ittuu zuuzummina, wodhiyaa kiitanchchaan unttuntta dhayisseeddawaadan zuuzummoppite. \x - \xo 10:10 \xt Pay 16:41-49\x* 
\p  
\v 11 Hawe ubbay haratussi timirtte gidanaadan unttunttu bolla gakkeedda. Qassi nuuna wodiyaa wurssethay gakkana mateeddawantta seeranaw xaafetteedda. 
\p  
\v 12 Hewaa diraw, minna eqqaaddi giide qoppiyaa uray ooninne kunddennaadan, barena naago.  
\v 13 Hinttentta gakkiyaa paacii, asaa ubbaa gakkiyaa paaciyaa malappe attin, aynne dummatenna. Hinttenttu wolqqay danddayiyaawaappe aadhdhiyaa paaciyaan hintte paacettanaw koyyenna Xoossay ammanetteeddawaa. Shin hinttentta paacii gakkiyaa wode, he paaciyaa I hinttentta danddayissana. Qassi he paaciyaappe hinttenttu kesiyaa ogiyaakka I immana. 
\p  
\v 14 Hewaa diraw, ta dosiyaawanttoo, eeqaw goyinnoppite.  
\v 15 Hinttenttu wozanaama asaa gideedda diraw, taani hinttenttoo oday. Taani giyaawaa hintte pirddite.  
\v 16 Nuuni Xoossaa galatiide shaakkiyaa anjjuwaa xuu7ay Kiristtoosa suuthaanna ittippetethay de7iyaawaa gidennee? Qassi nuuni menthiyaa ukithay Kiristtoosa ashuwaanna ittippetethay de7iyaawaa gidennee?  
\v 17 Itti ukithay de7iyaa diraw, nuuni cora gidooppekka, itti asatetha. Ayissi gooppe, nuuni ubbaykka he itti ukithaa shaaketteetto. 
\p  
\v 18 Israa7eeliyaa asaa xeellite. Yarshshuwaa miyaawanttu yarshshiyaasaanna ittippetethay de7iyaawantta gidikkinoo? \x - \xo 10:18 \xt Wog 7:6\x* 
\v 19 Simmi taani waagaytaa? Eeqaassi yarshshetteedda qumay maaddii woy eeqay maaddii?  
\v 20 Maaddenna; shin taani giyaawe Xoossaa ammanenna asatuu iita ayyaanatuwassi yarshshiyaawaappe attin, Xoossaw yarshshikkino. Iita ayyaanatuwaanna hintte ittippe zuppetana mala, taani koyyikke. \x - \xo 10:20 \xt Zar 32:17\x* 
\v 21 Godaa xuu7aappe ushiidde qassi iita ayyaanatuwaa xuu7aappe ushanaw hintte danddayikkita. Godaa gaytaappe hintte gishettiidde qassi iita ayyaanatuwaa gaytaappe maanaw danddayikkita.  
\v 22 Hewaa udiide nuuni Godaanna xiinottanaw koshshii? Nuuni aappe minneettoo? \x - \xo 10:22 \xt Zar 32:21\x* 
\p  
\v 23 Hintteppe ittu ittuu, “Ubbabaa oothanaw taana diggiyaabay baawa”; shin ubbabay maaddenna. “Ubbabaa oothanaw diggiyaabay baawa; shin ubbabay geeshshenna” yaagiino.  
\v 24 Ooninne hara asaa maaddiyaabaa qoppoppe attin, haray atto ittuunne barena maaddiyaabaa qoppoppo. 
\p  
\v 25 Geyaan axaare taraan zali77ettiyaa ashuwaa hintte wozanaa qofaan, aynne sidhennaan miite.  
\v 26 Ayissi gooppe, alamiinne aani de7iyaabay ubbay Godaabaa. \x - \xo 10:26 \xt Maz 24:1\x* 
\p  
\v 27 Itti ammanenna asay hinttentta immatha udi shoobbanaw xeesina baanaw koyyooppe, hintte wozanaa qofaan, aynne sidhennaan hintte sintha I aathiyaabaa ubbaa miite.  
\v 28 Shin itti uray hinttenttoo, “Hawe eeqaw yarshsheeddawaa” gooppe, he hinttenttoo odeedda bitaniyaa dirawunne qassi hintte wozanaa qofaa diraw, he qumaa mooppite.  
\v 29 Taani giyaawe ne wozanaa qofaa diraassa gidenna; shin yokko bitaniyaa wozanaa qofaa diraassa. 
\p Taani ta hananaw danddayiyaa ta hanotaa hara asaa wozanay ayaw pirddii?  
\v 30 Taani Xoossaa galataade qumaa mooppe, Xoossaa galataade meedda qumaw ayaw borettaytaa? 
\p  
\v 31 Simmi hintte ayaanne mooppe, woy ayaanne ushooppe, woy hintte ayaanne udooppe, ubbabaa Xoossaa bonchchuwaassi oothiite.  
\v 32 Hinttenttu Ayihuda asatuwaassi woy Giriike asatuwaassi woy Xoossaa ammaniyaawanttussi dhubo gidoppite.  
\v 33 Taani qassi coratuu attana mala, unttunttu ubbaa maaddanaadaanippe attin, ta huuphew maaduwaa koyyennaan, asaa ubbaa ubbabaani nashechchiyaawaadan, hinttenttukka hewaada udite. 
\c 11  
\p  
\v 1 Taani Kiristtoosa leemisuwaa kaalliyaawaadan, hinttenttukka tawaa kaallite. 
\s1 Asay Ittippe Woossiyaa Wode De7anaw Bessiyaa Wogaa 
\p  
\v 2 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hintte ubbabaani taana hassayiya dirawunne, wogaa taani hinttenttoo immeeddawaadan, hintte minissiide naagiyaa diraw, hinttentta galatay.  
\v 3 Shin Kiristtoosi attumawaa ubbaw huuphe gidiyaawaa, attuma asay macca asaassi huuphe gidiyaawaanne qassi Xoossay Kiristtoosassi huuphe gidiyaawaa hintte erana mala koyyay.  
\v 4 Xoossaa woossiidde, woy timbbitiyaa odiidde, bare huuphiyaa goozziyaa attuma asay ubbay Kiristtoosa toochchee.  
\v 5 Qassi Xoossaa woossaadde woy timbbitiyaa odaadde, bare huuphiyaa goozzenna maccawunna bare asinaa toochchaw; ayaw gooppe, iza bare huuphiyaa meedettadiggoonninna itti mala. 
\p  
\v 6 Maccawunna bare huuphiyaa goozzana dhayooppe, qanxxissu. Shin iza bare huuphiyaa qanxxissanawe woy meedissanawe pokkooppe, bare huuphiyaa goozzu.  
\v 7 Attumawe Xoossaa leemisuwanne bonchchuwaa gidiyaa diraw, bare huuphiyaa goozzanaw bessenna; shin maccawunna attumawaassi bonchcho. \x - \xo 11:7 \xt Dom 1:26-27\x* 
\v 8 Ayissi gooppe, maccawunna attumawaappe beettaadduppe attin, attumawe maccawunnippe beettibeenna. \x - \xo 11:8 \xt Dom 2:18-23\x* 
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, maccawunna attumawaa diraw medhettaadduppe attin, attumawe maccawunni diraw medhettibeenna.  
\v 10 Hewaa diraw, maccawunna bare asinaa ayissuwaappe garssanna de7iyaawaa erissanawunne kiitanchchatuwaa diraw, izi huuphiyan goozziyaabay de7anaw bessee. 
\p  
\v 11 Shin Godaan maccawunna attumawe baynnaan de7ukku; attumawekka maccawunna baynnaan de7enna.  
\v 12 Ayissi gooppe, maccawunna attumawaappe medhetteeddawaadan, qassi attumawekka maccawunnippe yeletteedda. Qassi ubbabaykka Xoossaappe yee. 
\p  
\v 13 Hinttenttu hintte huuphew pirddite. Maccawunna bare huuphiyaa goozzennaan Xoossaa woossanaw bessii?  
\v 14-15 Attumawe bare huuphiyaa dichchooppe, aw pokko. Shin maccawunna bare huuphiyaa dichchooppe, iziw bonchcho gidiyaawaa haray atto, medhetenttonne hinttentta tamaarissennee? Ayissi gooppe, maccawunni huuphii izo kammanaw iziw imetteedda.  
\v 16 Shin ooninne ha yewuwaan palumettanaw koyyooppe, nuussi gidina woy Xoossaa ammaniyaawanttoo gidinakka, hawaappe hara wogay baawa. 
\s1 Godaa Kawuwaa Akkiya Wogaa 
\r (Mat 26:26-29; Mar 14:22-25; Luq 22:14-20) 
\p  
\v 17 Hintte shiiqiyaawe iitabaassappe attin, lo77obaassa gidenna diraw, taani ha azazuwaa immaadde hinttentta galatikke.  
\v 18 Shin hintte woosa gollen shiiqiyaa wode, hintte giddon phalqqethay de7iyaawaa taani sisay. Qassi hewe itti bagganna tuma gidiyaawaa ammanay.  
\v 19 Ayissi gooppe, hintte matan ammanetteeddawanttu qoncci erettana mala, hintte giddonikka qassi shaakuu de7anaw bessee.  
\v 20 Hewaa diraw, hintte ittippe shiiqiyaa wode, hintte shiiquu Godaa kawuwaa maanaassa gidenna.  
\v 21 Ayissi gooppe, hintte qumaa miyaa wode, ubbay huuphiyan huuphiyan barewaa barewaa miyaa diraw, ittuu koshattee; ittuu qassi mathottee.  
\v 22 Maanawunne ushanaw hinttenttoo golli baawee? Woy Xoossaa woosa golliyaa kadhiitee? Qassi aynnee baynnawantta yeellayiitee? Taani hinttentta waagoo? Ha yewuwaan taani hinttentta galatoo? Galatikke. 
\p  
\v 23 Ayissi gooppe, taani qassi hinttenttoo immeedda timirttiyaa Godaappe akkaaddi. Godaa Yesuusi unttunttu A aathiide immeedda qamma daabbuwaa akkiide, \x - \xo 11:23 \xt Mat 26:26-28; Mar 14:22-24; Luq 22:19,20\x* 
\v 24 Xoossaa galateedda; daabbuwaa menthiide, “Heyte; miite. Hawe hintte gishshataw barena immeedda ta ashuwaa. Hawaan taana qoppite” yaageedda.  
\v 25 Hawaadankka, kawuwaa miide simmina, xuu7aa qassi akkiide, “Hawe xuu7ay ta suuthaan taani caaqqeedda ooratha caaquwaa. Hinttenttu aappe usheedda wode ubbaan hewaan taana qoppite” yaageedda. \x - \xo 11:25 \xt Kes 24:6-8; Erm 31:31-34\x* 
\v 26 Ayissi gooppe, hintte ha daabbuwaa meedda wode ubbaaninne ha xuu7aappe usheedda wode ubbaan Goday yaana gakkanawukka, A hayquwaa odiita. 
\p  
\v 27 Hewaa diraw, bessennaan de7iidde Godaa daabbuwaa miyaawe, woy Godaa xuu7aappe ushiyaawe ooninne A ashuwaanne A suuthaa acotee.  
\v 28 Shin asay bare huuphiyaa paacco. Yaatiide daabbuwaa mo. Xuu7aappekka usho.  
\v 29 Ayissi gooppe, Godaa ashuwaa shaakkiide erennaan daabbuwaa miyaawenne xuu7aappekka ushiyaawe bare huuphewa pirddaa meennee ushee.  
\v 30 Hewaa diraw, hintte giddon coratuu daaburanchchanne hargganchcha gideeddino; qassi unddenneeddawanttu hayqqeeddino.  
\v 31 Shin nuuni nu huuphiyaa tumu paacceeddentto, Xoossay nuuna pirddenna.  
\v 32 Nuuni pirddettiyaa wode, ha alamiyaanna ittippe pirddettenna mala, Goday nuuna seeree. 
\p  
\v 33 Hewaa diraw, taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, Godaa kawuwaa maanaw hintte shiiqiyaa wode, ittu ittuwaa naagite.  
\v 34 Ooninne koshatteeddawaa gidooppe, ittippe shiiqiyaa wode Xoossaa pirddan hintte gelenna mala, bare soyin mo. 
\p Atteeddawaa taani yaa baade giigissana. 
\c 12  
\s1 Geeshsha Ayyaanaa Imotatuwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, Geeshsha Ayyaanaa imotaabaa hintte eranaw koyyay.  
\v 2 Hinttenttu Xoossaa ammanenna wode, ubba wode kaalliyaawaadankka, haasayenna eeqatuwaakko hintte beeddawaa eriita.  
\v 3 Hewaa diraw, Xoossaa Ayyaanay kaalethiyaa asay ooninne, “Yesuusi sheqetto” yaagiide haasayeennawaanne qassi Geeshsha Ayyaanay kaalethooppeppe attin, haray atto itti asaynne, “Yesuusi Godaa” gaanaw danddayennawaa taani hinttentta erissay. 
\p  
\v 4 Ayyaanaa imotay dumma dumma; shin immiyaa Ayyaanay ittuwaa. \x - \xo 12:4 \xt Rom 12:6-8\x* 
\v 5 Qassi oothiyaa oosuu dumma dumma; shin Goday ittuwaa.  
\v 6 Oosuwaa oothanaw dumma dumma ogii de7ishshin, he oothiyaa ogiyaa ubbaa asaa ubbaw qonccissiyaa Xoossay ittuwaa.  
\v 7 Shin asaa ubbaa maaddanaw, Geeshsha Ayyaanaa qonccissiyaa wolqqay ubbaw huuphiyan huuphiyan imetteedda. 
\p  
\v 8 Ayissi gooppe, Geeshsha Ayyaanay ittuwaassi aadho eratethaa haasayaa immeedda; qassi ittuwaassi eratethaa haasayaa immeedda.  
\v 9 He Geeshsha Ayyaanay ittuwaassi ammanuwaa immiide, yokkowassi hargganchchaa pathiyaa wolqqaa immeedda.  
\v 10 Geeshsha Ayyaanay ittuwaassi malaataa oothiyaa wolqqaa immiide, ittuwaassi timbbitiyaa odiyaa wolqqaa immeedda. Ittuwaassi ayyaanatuwaa gidduwan de7iyaa dummatethaa eriyaa wolqqaa immiide, ittuwaassi dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaa wolqqaa immeedda. Qassi ittuwaassi dumma dumma qaalaan haasayeeddawaa billiyaa wolqqaa immeedda  
\v 11 Shin ha ubbabaa oothiyaawe he itti Geeshsha Ayyaanaa. Asaa ubbaw I bare koyyiyaawaadan, dumma dumma imotaa shaakki shaakkiide immeedda. 
\s1 Itti Bollaan De7iyaa Dumma Dumma Asatethatuwaa 
\p  
\v 12 Kiristtoosi cora asatethatuu de7iyaa itti bollaa mala. Bollay cora asatethatuwaappe medhetteeddawaa gidooppekka, itti bollaa. \x - \xo 12:12 \xt Rom 12:4-5\x* 
\v 13 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni Ayihuda asaa gidooppenne woy Giriike asaa gidooppe, woy aylle gidooppenne woy womanno gidooppe, ubbay itti Geeshsha Ayyaanaan itti bollaa gidanaw xammaqetteeddo. Qassi nuuni ubbay itti Geeshsha Ayyaanaa usheeddo. 
\p  
\v 14 Ayissi gooppe, bollaassi asatethay cora gidiyaawaappe attin, ittuwaa gidenna.  
\v 15 Gedi, “Taani kushiyaa gidenna diraw, bollaa qommo gidikke” gooppe, I hewaa giyaawe bollaa qommo gidiyaawaa digganee?  
\v 16 Haythaykka, “Taani ayfiyaa gidenna diraw, bollaa qommo gidikke” gooppe, I hewaa giyaawe bollaa qommo gidiyaawaa digganee?  
\v 17 Bollay ubbay ayfiyaa xalalaa gidintto, wootiide sisanaw danddayii? Qassi bollay ubbay haythaa xalalaa gidintto, wootiide singganaw danddayii? 
\p  
\v 18 Shin Xoossay bare koyyeeddawaadan, bollaa asatethatuwaa ittuwaa ittuwaa bollan wotheedda.  
\v 19 Ubbay itti qommo gidintto, bollay haqan de7anee?  
\v 20 Shin asatethatuu cora gidooppekka, bollay ittuwaa. 
\p  
\v 21 Ayifii kushiyaa, “Neeni taana koshshakka” gaanaw danddayenna. Woy qassi huuphii gedatuwaa, “Hinttenttu taana koshshikkita” gaanaw danddayenna.  
\v 22 Shin laafa malatiyaa bollaa asatethatuu loythi koshshiyaawantta.  
\v 23 Bollaa asatethatuwaappe bonchchettennawantta nuussi malatiyaawantta nuuni loythi bonchcheetto. Qassi nuuna yeellayiyaa bollaa asatethatuwaakka loythi bonchcheetto.  
\v 24 Nu bollaappe beettiyaa baggaw mayuu koshshenna; shin pokkiyaa bagga asatethatuwaa loythi mayizzanaadan, Xoossay asatethaa ittippe gatheedda.  
\v 25 Bollaa asatethatuu ittu ittuwaassi itti mala qofaa qoppanaappe attin, bollaan dummatethay de7anaw bessenna.  
\v 26 Bollaa asatethatuwaappe ittuu seelettooppe, bollaa asatethatuu ubbaykka aananna seelettiino; bollaa asatethatuwaappe ittuu bonchchettooppe, bollaa asatethatuu ubbay aananna nashettiino. 
\p  
\v 27 Hinttenttu ubbay Kiristtoosa bollaa; qassi huuphiyan huuphiyan hintte ubbaykka A bollaa asatethatuwaa.  
\v 28 Xoossay woosa gollen itti itti asatuwaa, koyruwaan Yesuusi kiitteeddawantta, laa7enthuwan nabatuwaa, heezzenthuwan tamaarissiyaawantta, hewaappe guyyiyan, malaataa oothiyaawantta, hewaappe guyyiyan, pathiyaa wolqqay de7iyaawantta, maaddiyaawantta, woosa golliyaa ayissiyaawantta dumma dumma qaalaan haasiyaawantta ootheedda. \x - \xo 12:28 \xt Efe 4:11\x* 
\v 29 Ubbatuu Yesuusi kiitteeddawanttee? Ubbatuu nabatee? Ubbatuu tamaarissiyaawanttee? Ubbatuu malaataa oothiinoo?  
\v 30 Ubbaassi pathiyaa wolqqay de7ii? Ubbatuu dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiinoo? Qassi dumma dumma qaalaan haasayeeddawaa ubbatuu billiinoo?  
\v 31 Shin ubbaappe aadhdhiyaa imotaa loythi koyyite. 
\p Qassi ubbaappe loythi aadhdhiyaa ogiyaa taani hinttentta bessana. 
\c 13  
\s1 Tumu Siiquwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taani asaa qaalaaninne kiitanchchaa qaalaan haasayooppekka taw siiquu dhayooppe, ta hasayay coo waassiyaa dawalaa mala; woy qolccakattiyaa xinaaxiliyaa mala.  
\v 2 Nabetethaa imotay taw de7ooppekka, taani geemmeedda yewuwaa ubbaanne eratethaa ubbaa erinttokka, qassi deriyaa denthi diggiyaa ammanuu taw de7ooppekka, siiquu dhayooppe, taani ayaanne gidikke. \x - \xo 13:2 \xt Mat 17:20; 21:21; Mar 11:23\x* 
\v 3 Taw de7iyaawaa ubbaa hiyyeesatuwaa mizanaw imminttokka haray atto, ta bollaa tamaan guuddanaw aatha imminttokka siiquu dhayooppe, taana aynne maaddenna. 
\p  
\v 4 Siiquu danddayanchchaa. Siiquu keekee. Siiquu qanaatenna. Ceeqettenna; qassi otorettenna.  
\v 5 Siiquu barew bessennawaa oothenna; Uzettenna; Yilotenna; Siiquu naaqetteeddawaakka paydenna.  
\v 6 Siiquu tumatethaan nashettiyaawaappe attin, wordduwan nashettenna.  
\v 7 Siiquu ubbabaa danddayee. Ubbabaykka hananawaa giide, nashechchaan naagee. Ubbabaani genccee. 
\p  
\v 8 Siiquu mulekka dhayenna. Shin nabetethaykka attana. Dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaawekka attana. Eratethaykka dhayana.  
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni eratethaappe pacaa ereetto; timbbitiyaappekka pacaa odeetto.  
\v 10 Shin kumentha gideeddawe yiyaa wode, pacay dhayana. 
\p  
\v 11 Taani na7atethaan de7iyaa wode, na7aadan haasayay. Na7adan qoppay. Qassi na7adankka akeekay. Wodalla gideedda wode, na7atethaa hanuwaa aggaaddi.  
\v 12 Nuuni ha77i be7iyaawe masttootiyan be7iyaa lem77i lem77iyaa malaa mala; shin he wode nuuni nu ayfiyaan qoncciyaan be7ana. Ha77i taani eratethaappe pacaa eray; shin Xoossay taana wurssiide eriyaawaadan, he wode taanikka wurssa erana. 
\p  
\v 13 Shin hewaa gidooppe, ammanuu, hananawaa giide nashechchaan naagiyaawenne siiquu, hawanttu heezzatuu minniide de7iino. Hawanttuppe aadhdhiyaawe siiquwaa. 
\c 14  
\s1 Geeshsha Ayyaanaa Imotaanne Unttunttu Maaduwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Siiquwaa kaallite. Ayyaanaa imotaakka loythi koyyite. Shin ubbaappe aathiide, nabetethaa koyyite.  
\v 2 Ayissi gooppe, dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaa uray Xoossaw haasayeeppe attin, asaassi haasayenna. Ayissi gooppe, I haasayiyaawaa ooninne akeekenna. Shin asaassi qonccibeenna yewuwaa Ayyaanaa wolqqaan haasayee.  
\v 3 Shin nabii asaa maaddanaw, zoranawunne minissanaw asaassi haasayee.  
\v 4 Dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaa uray barena maaddee. Shin nabii woosa golliyaa maaddee. 
\p  
\v 5 Hinttenttu ubbay dumma dumma qaalaan hasayaanawaa taani dosay. Shin nabetethaa hewaappe aathaade dosay. Ayissi gooppe, dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaawe he haasayeeddawaa woosa golliyaa maaddanaw billiyaa asay dhayooppe, dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaawaappe nabetethay aadhdhee. 
\p  
\v 6 Shin taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, ha77i taani hinttenttukko baade, dumma dumma qaalaan haasayaadde, saxaan woy eratethaan woy nabetethaan woy tamaarissiyaawaan hinttenttussi odana dhayooppe, taani hinttentta ayaa maaddaytaa?  
\v 7 Haray atto, shemppuu baynnabay suusulliyaa gidina woy diithaa gidina kaa7iidde, bare kaassaa dummatethaa erissana dhayooppe, suusulliyaa punnooppenne, woy diithaa diixxooppe, asay wootiide eranee?  
\v 8 Qassi xurumbbaa waasuu loythi erettana dhayooppe, olaw oonee giigettanawee?  
\v 9 Hawaadankka, qassi dumma dumma qaalaan hintte haasaayiyaawe qoncce gidennaan dhayooppe, hintte haasayiyaawaa asay wooti akeekanee? Ayissi gooppe, carkkuwaassi hintte haasayiita. 
\p  
\v 10 Ha alamiyaan cora qaalay de7ee; shin bilethay baynna qaalay ittuunne baawa.  
\v 11 Shin itti asay haasayiyaa qaalaa taani erana dhayooppe, he haasayiyaawe taw imathaa gidee; taanikka aw imathaa giday.  
\v 12 Hawaadankka, qassi Geeshsha Ayyaanaa imotaa hintte akkanaw loythi koyyiyaawantta gidiyaa diraw, woosa golliyaa dichchanaw maaddawaa ubbabaappe aathiide koyyite. 
\p  
\v 13 Hewaa diraw, dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaawe bare haasayeeddawaa billanaw danddayana mala, Xoossaa woosso.  
\v 14 Ayissi gooppe, taani dumma dumma qaalaan Xoossaa woossooppe, ta ayyaanaykka woossee; shin ta garssa qofay aynne go77ettenna.  
\v 15 Yaatina, taani wootoo? Taani ta ayyaanan Xoossaa woossana; qassi ta qofankka Xoossaa woossana. Ta ayyaanan yexxana; qassi ta qofankka yexxana.  
\v 16 Hewaa gidana dhayooppe, neeni ne ayyaanaa xalalaan Xoossaa galatiyaawaa gidooppe, he sa7aan neeni giyaawaa erenna asay neeni Xoossaa galatiyaawaa erennaan, neeni galateeddawaan wootiide, “Amen77i” gaanee?  
\v 17 Neeni Xoossaa galatiyaawe lo77a; shin hewe yokko bitaniyaa maaddenna. 
\p  
\v 18 Taani dumma dumma qaalaan hintte ubbaappe aathaade haasayiyaa diraw, Xoossaa galatay.  
\v 19 Shin taani woosa gollen haratuwaa tamaarssanaw dumma dumma qaalaan tammu sha77a qaalatuwaa haasayiyaawaappe ichcheshu qaalatuwaa ta wozanaa qofaan haasayanaw dosay. 
\p  
\v 20 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hintte iita yewuwaan guutha naanaa mala gidanaappe attin, qofaan guutha naanaa mala gidoppite; hintte garssa qofaan wozanaamatuwaa gidite.  
\v 21 Xoossaa Maxaafan, 
\q1 “Goday, ‘Taani ha asaw, 
\q2 dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaa asaaninne 
\q2 imathatuwaa doonaan haasayana. 
\q1 Shin hewankka, 
\q2 taani giyaawaa unttunttu sisikkino’ yaagee” 
\m geetettiide xaafetteedda. \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Isa 28:11-12\x* 
\p  
\v 22 Simmi dumma dumma qaalaan haasaayiyaawe ammanennawanttussi malaata gidiyaawaappe attin, ammaniyaawanttussi malaata gidenna. Qassi nabatuwaappe haasayettiyaawe ammaniyaawanttussi malaata gidiyaawaappe attin, ammanennawanttussi malaata gidenna. 
\p  
\v 23 Hewaa diraw, ammaniyaa asay ubbay ittippe shiiqiide, qassi ubbaykka dumma dumma qaalaan haasayooppe, tamaaribeenna asay woy ammanenna asay geliide, hinttentta ubbaa, “Gooyiita” geennee?  
\v 24 Shin tamaaribeenna asay woy ammanenna asay woosa golle geliyaa wode, asay ubbay timbbitiyaa odooppe, I bare sisiyaawaan bare nagaraa akeekee. Qassi he siseeddabaa ubbankka I pirddettana.  
\v 25 A wozanaan geemmeedda qofaykka qonccana. Hawaadankka qassi, “Xoossay tumu hintte giddon de7ee” yaagiide markkattiidde, guufanniide Xoossaw goyinnana. 
\s1 Asay Ittippe Woossiyaa Wode De7anaw Bessiyaa Wogaa 
\p  
\v 26 Simmi taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, ayee? Hinttenttu ittippe shiiqiyaa wode, huuphiyan huuphiyan, ittuwaassi mazimuri de7ee; ittuwaassi tamaarissiyaawe de7ee; ittuwaassi saxay de7ee; qassi ittuwaassi dumma dumma qaalaan haasaayiyaawe de7ee; ittuwaassi billiyaawe de7ee. Ubbaykka woosa golliyaa maaddiyaawaa gidanaw bessee.  
\v 27 Ooninne dumma dumma qaalaan haasayooppe, laa77u gidiide, woy darooppe heezzu gidiide, kaallaan kaallaan haasayanaw bessee. Qassi hara ittuu unttunttu haasayeeddawaa billo.  
\v 28 Shin billiyaa asay dhayooppe, dumma dumma qaalaan haasayiyaawe woosa golliyaan co77u go. Bare huuphewunne Xoossaw haasayo. 
\p  
\v 29 Nabatuukka laa77u gidiide woy heezzu gidiide haasayino. Qassi haranttu unttunttu giyaawaa shaakkino.  
\v 30 Shin Xoossay he sa7aan utteedda haraassi ittibaa qonccissooppe, kasenna haasayiyaawe co77u go.  
\v 31 Ayissi gooppe, ubbay tamaarana malanne ubbay minnana mala, kaallaan kaallaan timbbitiyaa odanaw danddayiita.  
\v 32 Timbbitiyaa odiyaawanttu imotay unttunttoo azazettee.  
\v 33 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay sarotethaa Xoossaappe attin, cabbuwaa Xoossaa gidenna. 
\p Geeshshatuu woosa golletuwaa ubbaan,  
\v 34 maccawanttu shiiquwaa garssan co77u giino. Ayissi gooppe, Ayihudatuwaa higgii giyaawaadankka unttunttu moodettanaappe attin, shiiquwaa garssan haasayanaw unttunttoo maati baawa.  
\v 35 Maccawanttu shiiquwaa garssan haasaayiyaawe pokko gidiyaa diraw, ayentto eranaw koyyooppenne soyin barenttu asinaa oochchino. 
\p  
\v 36 Xoossaa qaalay koyro hintteppe yeeddee? Woy hintte xalalaakko yeeddee?  
\v 37 Ooninne barena nabiyaa woy Xoossaa Ayyaanay de7iyaa asaa yaagiide qoppooppe, taani hinttenttoo xaafiyaawe Godaa azazuwaa gidiyaawaa akeeko.  
\v 38 Shin ooninne akeekana dhayooppe, akeekoppo bashi aggo. 
\p  
\v 39 Hewaa diraw, taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, timbbitiyaa odanaw loythi amottite. Qassi dumma dumma qaalaan haasiyaawaakka diggoppite.  
\v 40 Shin ubbabaykka wogaaninne maaran hano. 
\c 15  
\s1 Kiristtoosi Hayquwaappe Denddeeddabaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani hinttenttoo odeedda mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa hintte akkeeddawaanne qassi hintte ammanuu aani eqqeeddawaa hinttentta qopethay.  
\v 2 Hinttenttu ammanuu mela gidana dhayooppe, qassi taani hinttenttoo odeedda qaalaa loythi oyqqooppe, hintte he mishiraachchuwaa qaalaan atteeddita. 
\p  
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, taani qassi akkeeddawaa ubbabaappe aadhdhiide koshshiyaawaa kasetaade hinttenttussi immaaddi. Hewe ayee gooppe, Xoossaa maxaafay giyaawaadan, Kiristtoosi nu nagaraa diraw \x - \xo 15:3 \xt Isa 53:5-12\x* 
\v 4 hayqqiide moogetteedda. Xoossaa Maxaafay giyaawaadankka, heezzenthiyaa gallassi hayquwaappe \x - \xo 15:4 \xt Maz 16:8-10; Mat 12:40; Kit 2:24-32\x* 
\v 5 denddiide, Phexiroosaw qoncceedda. Hewaappe guyyiyan, bare kiitteedda tammanne laa77atoo qoncceedda. \x - \xo 15:5 \xt Mat 28:16-17; Mar 16:14; Luq 24:34,36; Yoh 20:19\x* 
\v 6 Hewaappe guyyiyan, ichcheshu xeetuwaappe dariya barena kaalliyaa asaw itti kaalla qoncceedda. Unttunttuppe dariya baggay hanno gakkanaassikka paxa de7iino; shin amareeddawanttu hayqqeeddino.  
\v 7 Hewaappe guyyiyan, Yayiqoobaw qoncceedda; guyyeppe bare kiitteedda ubbatoo qoncceedda. 
\p  
\v 8 Qassi ubbaappe wurssethaan, wodii gakkennaan yeletteedda tawukka qoncceedda. \x - \xo 15:8 \xt Kit 9:3-6\x* 
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, Yesuusi kiitteedda ubbaappe taani laafa; taani Xoossaa woosa golliyaa waayisseedda diraw, Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa geetettaade xeesettanawukka bessikke.  
\v 10 Shin Xoossaa aadho keekatethaan taani taanakka. Qassi taw I immeedda aadho keekatethay mela gidibeenna; shin taani unttuntta ubbaappe aathaade oothaaddi. Shin taananna de7iyaa Xoossaa aadho keekatethay ootheeddappe attin, taana gidikke.  
\v 11 Simmi taana gidooppekka, woy unttuntta gidooppekka, nuuni ubbay odiyaawe hawaa; hinttenttukka hawaa ammaneeddita. 
\s1 Asay Hayquwaappe Denddanabaa 
\p  
\v 12 Kiristtoosi hayquwaappe denddeeddawaa odiyaawaa gidooppe, hinttenttuppe itti itti asatuu yaatina wootiide, “Hayqqeedda asay hayquwaappe denddenna” yaagiinoo?  
\v 13 Hayqqeedda uray hayquwaappe denddibeennawaa gidooppe, yaatina hekko Kiristtoosikka hayquwaappe denddibeenna giyaawaa.  
\v 14 Kiristtoosi hayquwaappe denddibeennawaa gidooppe, yaatina nuuni odiyaawekka mela; qassi hintte ammanuukka mela.  
\v 15 Qassi nuuni, “Kiristtoosa hayquwaappe dentheedda” yaagiide Xoossaabaa markkatteedda diraw, A worddo markkatuwaa gidiide beetteeddo. Shin hayqqeeddawantta hayquwaappe I denthibeennawaa gidooppe, Kiristtoosakka denthibeenna.  
\v 16 Ayissi gooppe, hayqqeeddawanttu hayquwaappe denddennawaa gidooppe, simmi Kiristtoosikka denddibeenna.  
\v 17 Kiristtoosi hayquwaappe denddibeennawaa gidooppe, hintte ammanuukka mela; qassi hintte hawaa gakkanawukka nagaraanna de7iita.  
\v 18 Simmi Kiristtoosa ammaniide hayqqeeddawanttukka qassi dhayeeddino giyaawaa.  
\v 19 Nuuni ha de7uwaa xalalaw Kiristtoosan hidooteedda \f + \fr 15:19 \fq hidootaa: \ft Kiristtoosan nu wotheedda nu ubbaa hidootay, ha alamiyaan de7uwaassa gidooppe, ha alamiyaan de7iyaa hara asatuwaa ubbaappekka nubay aadhdhiide iita, guussaa.\f* gidooppe, ha alamiyaan de7iyaa asaa ubbaappekka nubay lo77enna. 
\p  
\v 20 Shin Kiristtoosi hayqqeeddawanttu dendduwaassi bayra gidiide, hayquwaappe denddeeddawe tuma.  
\v 21 Ayissi gooppe, hayquu itti asaa bagganna ha alamiyaa yeedda, hayqqeeddawanttu dendduukka qassi itti asaa bagganna yeedda.  
\v 22 Ayissi gooppe, asay ubbay Addaamanna ittippetethaa medhdheedda diraw hayqqeeddawaadan, Kiristtoosanna ittippetethaa medhdheedda diraw, ubbay de7uwaassi denddana.  
\v 23 Shin ubbaykka bare kaallaan kaallaan denddana. Kiristtoosi ubbaappe kasetiide denddeedda; hewaappe guyyiyan, Kiristtoosawanttu Kiristtoosi yiyaa wode denddana. 
\p  
\v 24 Hewaappe guyyiyan, Kiristtoosi maataa ubbaa, godatethaa ubbaanne woliqqaa ubbaa dhayissiide, Xoossaw bare Aabboo kawutethaa immiyaa wode, wodiyaa wurssethay yaanawaa.  
\v 25 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay A morkketuwaa ubbaa A gediyaappe garssanna wothana gakkanaw, Kiristtoosi mooddanaw bessee. \x - \xo 15:25 \xt Maz 110:1\x* 
\v 26 Ubbaappe wurssethaan dhayiidde de7iyaa morkkii hayquwaa.  
\v 27 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Xoossay ubbabaa A gediyaappe garssanna wothiide moodisseedda” yaagee. Shin ubbabaa A gediyaappe garssanna wothiide moodisseedda giyaa wode, ubbabaa ootheedda Xoossaappe attin, yokko ubbay moodetteedda giyaawe qoncce. \x - \xo 15:27 \xt Maz 8:6\x* 
\v 28 Shin ubbabay Kiristtoosaw moodetteeddawaappe guyyiyan, Kiristtoosi qassi bare huuphew ubbabaa barena moodisseedda Xoossaw moodettana. Xoossay qassi ubbabaa wurssiide mooddana. 
\p  
\v 29 Hewaa gidana dhayooppe, hayqqeeddawanttu kotaa xammaqettiyaawanttu ayaa oothiinoo? Hayqqeeddawanttu ubbakka denddennawaa gidooppe, asay hayqqeeddawanttu kotaa ayissi xammaqettii? 
\p  
\v 30 Yaatina, nuuni ubba wode ayissi hassayenna metuwan geleettoo?  
\v 31 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani nu Godaa Kiristtoosa Yesuusan taw de7iyaa hinttenan ceeqettaadde, gallassaan gallassaan hayqqay.\x - \xo 15:31 \xt Isa 22:13\x* 
\v 32 Taani Efesoonen asaa qofaadan du7aanna baaxeteeddawe taana ayaa maaddii? Shin hayqqeeddawanttu hayquwaappe denddennawaa gidooppe, 
\q1 “Simmi moyttennee ushoytte; 
\q2 ayissi gooppe, nuuni wontti hayqqana” giyaawaa mala. 
\p  
\v 33 Cimettoppite; iita laggetethay lo77o hanotaa bayizzee.  
\v 34 Xillotethaakko simmite. Nagaraa oothoppite. Hinttenttuppe itti itti asay Xoossaa erenna; taani hawaa hinttentta yeellayanaw gay. 
\s1 Hayquwaappe Denddeedda Bollaa Hanotaa 
\p  
\v 35 Shin itti asay, “Hayqqeedda asay waaniide denddanee? Unttunttu ayaa mala bollaanna yaanee?” yaagennaan aggenna.  
\v 36 Neenoo eeyaw, neeni gadiyan zeriyaa zerethay hayqqennan mokkenna.  
\v 37 Neeni zeriyaawe zarggaa gidina woy hara qommo kathaa gidina, ayfiyaa xalalaappe attin, lammi doliide kesiyaawaa gidenna.  
\v 38 Shin Xoossay zerethaw bare doseedda bollaa immee; qassi zerethaa ubbaassikka huuphiyan huuphiyan unttunttu bollaa immee.  
\v 39 Medhetaa ubbaa ashuu ittuwaa gidenna. Shin asaa ashuu ittuwaa; mehiyaa ashuu dumma; kafatuwaa ashuukka dumma; qassi moliyaa ashuukka dumma. 
\p  
\v 40 Qassi saluwaa asatethatuunne sa7aa asatethatuu de7iino. Shin saluwaa bollaa bonchchuu dumma; qassi sa7aa bollaa bonchchuu dumma.  
\v 41 Awayfiyaassi A huuphe bonchchuu de7ee. Agenaassikka A huuphe bonchchuu de7ee. Qassi xoolinttatuwassikka dumma bonchchuu de7ee; ayaw gooppe, itti xoolinttii yokko xoolinttiyaappe bonchchuwan dummatee. 
\p  
\v 42 Qassi hayqqeeddawanttu hayquwaappe denddiyaa wode hewaadan hanana; hayqqiyaa bollay moogettiide, hayqqenna bollaa gidiide denddana.  
\v 43 Bollay tooshiyan moogettiide, bonchchuwan denddana. Qassi daaburaan moogettiide, wolqqaan denddana.  
\v 44 Medhetaa bollay moogettiide, Geeshsha Ayyaanan kaalesettiyaa bollaa gidiide denddana. Medhetaa bollay de7ooppe, qassi Geeshsha Ayyaanaan kaalesettiyaa bollaykka de7ee. 
\p  
\v 45 Hawaadankka, qassi Xoossaa Maxaafan, “Koyro bitani, Addaami, paxa de7iyaa asa gidiide medhetteedda” yaagee. Shin wurssethaa Addaami de7uwaa immiyaa asa gideedda. \x - \xo 15:45 \xt Dom 2:7\x* 
\v 46 Shin medhetaa asay koyro yiina, geedoppe ayyaanaa asay yeeddappe attin, ayyaanaawe koyro yibeenna.  
\v 47 Koyro Addaami biittaappe medhetteedda; I biittaappe medhetteeddawaa. Laa7enthuwaa Addaami saluwaappe yeedda.  
\v 48 Ha sa7aa asatuu biittaappe medhetteeddawaa malatiino. Qassi saluwaa asatuu saluwaappe yeeddawaa malatiino.  
\v 49 Nuuni biittaappe medhetteeddawaa malaa mayyeeddawaadan, saluwaappe yeeddawaa malaakka qassi mayyana. 
\p  
\v 50 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani giyaawe hawaa; ashuunne suuthay \f + \fr 15:50 \ft Ha sa7aa bolla de7iidde asay mayyeedda ashuwaanne suuthaa, guussay ha alamiyaa asatethaa guussaa.\f* Xoossaa kawutethaa laattana danddayenna. Qassi wooqqiyaawe wooqqennawaa laattenna. 
\p  
\v 51-52 Sisite! Taani hinttenttoo ittibaa xuuray. Nuuni ubbay hayqqokko. Shin wurssethaa xurumbbay punettiyaa wode, lipheedda ayfii xeellanaassi wozanaa aathennaan laamettana. Ayissi gooppe, xurumbbay punettiyaa wode, hayqqeedda asay wooqqenna asa gidiide denddana; nuunikka laamettana. \x - \xo 15:51-52 \xt 1Te 4:15-17\x* 
\v 53 Ayissi gooppe, hawe wooqqiyaawe wooqqennawaa mayyanaw bessee; qassi hawe hayqqiyaawe hayqqennawaa mayyanaw bessee. 
\p  
\v 54 Shin hawe wooqqiyaawe wooqqennawaa mayyiyaa wode, qassi hawe hayqqiyaawe hayqqennawaa mayyiyaa wode, he wode, Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q2 “Hayquu xoonettiide mitetteedda. \x - \xo 15:54 \xt Isa 25:8\x* 
\q1  
\v 55 Hayqoo, ne yishshay haqanee? 
\q2 Hayqoo, ne xoonuu haqanee?” 
\m geedda qaalay polettana. \x - \xo 15:55 \xt Hos 13:14\x* 
\v 56 Hayquu dukkiyaa wolqqaa nagaraappe demmee; qassi nagaray wolqqaa higgiyaappe demmee.  
\v 57 Shin nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna nuuna xoonissiyaa Xoossaa galatay gakko. 
\p  
\v 58 Taani siiqiyaa taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hewaa diraw, qaaxxennaan minni eqqite. Hinttenttu daaburay Godaa bagganna mela gidennawaa eriide, ubba wode Godaa oosuwaa azallennan oothite. 
\c 16  
\s1 Yeerusalaamen De7iyaa Ammaniyaa Asaw Shiiqeedda Miishshaa Maaduwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Xoossaa asatoo miishshaa shiishshanaw Galatiyaan de7iyaa ammaniyaa asatoo taani qaalaa geleeddawaadan, hinttenttukka qassi hewaadan oothite.  
\v 2 Hinttenttu taani yaa biyaa wode, miishshaa shiishshenna mala, hintte ubbay Woggaa gallassi gallassi, hintte demmiyaa keenaappe hintte gollen dagayite.  
\v 3 Taani yaa gakkiyaa wode, hintte ammaniyaa asaa oona gidooppenne, hintte immeeddawaa gathana mala, dabidaabbiyaanna unttuntta Yeerusalaame kiittana.  
\v 4 Qassi taani unttunttunna baanaw koshshooppe, unttunttu taananna ittippe baanawantta. 
\s1 Phawuloosa Qofatuwaa 
\p  
\v 5 Taani Maqidooniyaanna aadhdhaadde, hinttenttukko baana; ayissi gooppe, taani Maqidooniyaanna aadhdhay.  
\v 6 Taani biyaasaa haqa gidooppenne, ta buussan hintte taana maaddana mala, hintte matan amareedda wodiyaa gami77ennaan aggikke. Woy balgguwaakka hintte matan shaaccennan waayya aggana.  
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, taani ha77i yaanna aadhdhaadde he ogiyaanna hinttentta be7anaw koyyikke. Goday gooppe, hintte matan amareedda wodiyaa takkanaw qoppay. 
\p  
\v 8 Shin taani Phenxxeqostte giyaa gallassay gakkanaw Efesoonen gami77ana.  
\v 9 Taw oosuu kumeedda aako penggiikka yaani dooyetteedda. Qassi taw cora morkketuu de7iino. 
\p  
\v 10 Ximootoose hinttenttukko yooppe, hintte matan I yayyennaan de7anaadan, A loythi oyqqite. Ayissi gooppe, ikka qassi Godaa oosuwaa oothee.  
\v 11 Hewaa diraw, ooninne A kadhoppo. Shin I taakko saro simmana mala, A maaddiide sarotethaan moyizzite. Ayissi gooppe, taani I ishatuwaanna simmanawaa naaga uttaaddi. 
\p  
\v 12 Shin nu ishaa Aphiloosi yokko ishatuwaanna hinttenttukko baana mala, taani A minissa woossaaddi. Shin ha77i hinttenttukko baanaw koyyibeenna; I barew miikkiyaa wode hinttenttukko baanawaa. 
\s1 Wurssethaa Zoriyaanne Sarotaa 
\p  
\v 13 Beegottite. Ammanuwan minni eqqite. Xalite. Goobite.  
\v 14 Oosuwaa ubbaa siiquwan oothite. 
\p  
\v 15-16 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, Isxxifaanoosinne A soy asay Giriiken koyro ammaneeddawantta gidiyaawaanne Xoossaa asatuwaassi oothanaw barentta immeeddawaa hintte eriita. Hinttenttukka unttunttu mala asaassinne, unttunttunna oothiyaa ubbaw daaburiyaa ubbaw eeno gaanaadan, taani hinttentta woossay. 
\p  
\v 17 Isxxifaanoosi, Parddonaaxisinne Akayqoosi hintte baynnasaan taana boorasissibeenna diraw, unttunttu yuussaan taani nashettay.  
\v 18 Unttunttu hinttentta ayyaanan minisseeddawaadan, taanakka ayyaanan minisseedda diraw, hewanttu mala asatuwaa dogoppite. 
\p  
\v 19 Iisiyan de7iyaa ammaniyaa asay hinttentta, “Saree, lo77ee” giino. Aqiilaynne Phirisqqilla barenttu soyin shiiqiyaa woosa golle asaannakka hinttenttoo Godaa sarotaa wozanaappe kiittiino.  
\v 20 Ishatuu ubbay hinttenttussi sarotaa kiittiino. 
\p Ittu ittuwaanna geeshsha yeretaa yerettiidde sarotettite.  
\v 21 Taani Phawuloosi ha sarotaa ta kushiyan xaafaaddi. 
\p  
\v 22 Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa siiqenna asay de7ooppe, I sheqetteeddawaa gido. Nu Godaw, haaya. 
\p  
\v 23 Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa aadho keekatethay hinttenttunna gido. 
\p  
\v 24 Kiristtoosa Yesuusan de7iyaa hinttenttu ubbaanna ta siiquu gido. Amen77i.